n class=\"relative bg-navy overflow-hidden pt-32 pb-20 sm:pt-40 sm:pb-24\"><div class=\"navy-grain absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-[0.03]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"hero-grid absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-[0.03]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute right-[-8rem] top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 pointer-events-none\" width=\"960\" height=\"960\" viewBox=\"-480 -480 960 960\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"0\" cy=\"0\" r=\"200\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-opacity=\"0.05\"></circle><circle cx=\"0\" cy=\"0\" r=\"340\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-opacity=\"0.05\"></circle><circle cx=\"0\" cy=\"0\" r=\"480\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-opacity=\"0.05\"></circle></svg><div class=\"container-main relative z-10\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl\"><nav aria-label=\"Fil d&#x27;Ariane\" class=\"mb-10\"><ol class=\"flex items-center flex-wrap gap-x-2 gap-y-1\"><li><a class=\"font-body text-xs text-white/35 hover:text-white/65 transition-colors\" href=\"/pt\">Início</a></li><li><span class=\"text-white/20 text-xs mx-1\">›</span></li><li><a class=\"font-body text-xs text-white/35 hover:text-white/65 transition-colors\" href=\"/pt/services\">Serviços</a></li><li><span class=\"text-white/20 text-xs mx-1\">›</span></li><li><span class=\"font-body text-xs text-white/60\" aria-current=\"page\">Gestão administrativa</span></li></ol></nav><span class=\"section-label text-champagne/70\">As nossas prestações</span><h1 class=\"font-display font-light text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.015em] text-white mt-2\">Gestão<!-- --> <span class=\"italic font-light text-champagne\">administrativa</span></h1><div class=\"w-10 h-px bg-champagne/30 my-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><p class=\"font-body text-white/58 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-lg mb-8\">Uma administração saudável é a base de uma empresa tranquila. Gerimos os seus fluxos administrativos diários com rigor para que nada seja deixado ao acaso.</p><a class=\"btn-primary\" href=\"/pt/contact\">Entrar em contacto<svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg></a></div></div></section><section class=\"relative bg-cream overflow-hidden\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 1440 80\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full\" style=\"height:var(--slant-h)\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><polygon points=\"0,0 1440,0 1440,80\" fill=\"#46184E\"></polygon></svg><div class=\"container-main pt-32 sm:pt-40 pb-24 sm:pb-32\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_288px] gap-16 items-start\"><div><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-light text-navy mb-10 leading-tight\">O que tratamos</h2><div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-6 py-7 border-b border-primary-100/40 last:border-b-0\"><span class=\"font-body text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-[0.14em] text-champagne w-5 shrink-0 mt-0.5 select-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\">01</span><div><p class=\"font-body font-semibold text-navy text-base leading-snug\">Faturação e gestão de pagamentos</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-6 py-7 border-b border-primary-100/40 last:border-b-0\"><span class=\"font-body text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-[0.14em] text-champagne w-5 shrink-0 mt-0.5 select-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\">02</span><div><p class=\"font-body font-semibold text-navy text-base leading-snug\">Acompanhamento de devedores e credores</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-6 py-7 border-b border-primary-100/40 last:border-b-0\"><span class=\"font-body text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-[0.14em] text-champagne w-5 shrink-0 mt-0.5 select-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\">03</span><div><p class=\"font-body font-semibold text-navy t